title: Fantasy Land Female Incantation Voices SFX
description: 281 sound files. A bundle of enchanting female voice pack including calm incantation, loud spells, whispery chanting, short vocals including sighs, with eathereal game/cinematic sound effects
longDescription:
A bundle of carefully crafted enchanting female voice pack including calm incantation, loud spells, whispery chanting, short vocals including sighs, with varying ethereal game/cinematic sound effects. Also includes a loop-able compound mix of dark spells as in nightmares.


Phrases are invented for this SFX pack which do not belong to any existing language.




Preview:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P_68jNbSAK0


A great asset for your game, mobile apps, motion graphics, films.


Should you wish to obtain the dry vocals, or have the SFX modified, or have more SFX tailor made (any Sound Effects actually!), please feel free to get in touch by emailing me at soundzblade@gmail.com
